      "title": "Ready to give quota if asked",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "If former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa wants to come to Parliament, he is ready to resign his MP position, Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna's National List MP Sita Arampebola said.",
        "However, so far neither the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna nor anyone else has made such a demand."
      ],
